Package HMS.Appointment

Class MedicalRecord

java.lang.Object
HMS.Appointment.MedicalRecord
public class MedicalRecord extends Object
Represents a medical record associated with an appointment within the healthcare management system. It holds comprehensive details about the patient's medical encounter including diagnosis and treatment.

      public MedicalRecord(String appointmentID, String patientID, String doctorID, LocalDateTime appointmentTime, String status, String diagnosis, String servicesProvided, String treatment, String prescription, String consultationNotes)
      Constructs a MedicalRecord with detailed information about a medical appointment.
      Parameters:
      appointmentID - Unique identifier for the appointment.
      patientID - Identifier of the patient.
      doctorID - Identifier of the doctor.
      appointmentTime - Time of the appointment.
      status - Current status of the medical record.
      diagnosis - Diagnosis made during the appointment.
      servicesProvided - Services provided during the appointment.
      treatment - Treatment prescribed.
      prescription - Prescription details.
      consultationNotes - Notes from the consultation.
